quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  77,46,"(E, jenumanja achimakafili!) Lyagani ni kusengwa panandi (mukandaŵi kannono kaumi wa duniyau), chisimu ŵanganyammwe ŵaleŵeleŵe."
  77,47,"Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila."
  77,48,"Soni pati iŵechetedwe kukwao (yanti): “Jinamani (kuswali).” Ngakwinamaga."
  79,37,"Sano mundu jwaŵasumbile mpika."
  79,38,"Ni kulongosya umi wa duniya."
  79,39,"Chisimu Moto Waukali basi ni liuto lyakwe."
  80,34,"Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachatila achimwenegwe."
  80,35,"Kwisa soni mamagwe ni babagwe."
  80,36,"Ni kwisa soni ŵankwakwe ni ŵanache ŵakwe."
  83,22,"Chisimu atenda ngoto tachiŵa m’chindimba (mu Mbepo Jakusengwasya)."
  83,23,"Ali pachanya pa indanda yetandiche chenene aku achilolaga (ku chindimba chaŵapele ni kum'bona soni Allah)."
  83,24,"Tinchikumanyilila pangope syao kumelemenda kwa chindimba."
  84,19,"Chisimu ŵanganyammwe chinsimanganeje nako kaŵe kane kutyochela pa kaŵe kane (paumi wa duniya uno mpaka kwa Akhera)."
  84,20,"Ana akwete chichi ŵanganyao chikwatendekasya kuti akakulupilila?"
  84,21,"Soni pati jichisoomedwaga kukwao Qur’an ŵangasujudu!"
  85,16,"Jwakutenda yajukusaka mwangalepeleka."
  85,17,"Ana jinyyiche abali ja mikutula ja asilikali?"
  85,18,"Achina Firiauna ni achina Samuda?"
  86,10,"Ni ngasakola (mundujo) machili galigose namuno nkulupusyo."
  86,11,"Ngukulumbila kwinani kwagwisyagwisya wula."
  86,12,"Ni ngulilumbila soni litaka lyaliganjikaga (pakoposya mmela)."
  87,7,"Ikaŵeje yasachile Allah, chisimu Jwalakwe jukumanyililaga yakuonechela ni yayikasasisika."
  87,8,"Ni chitun'jepepachisye litala lyakwalukangana (lyakutendela yambone)."
  87,9,"Basi kumbusyani naga kumbusyako tikuŵe kwakamuchisya."
  88,4,"Sichijinjila ku Moto Wakupoteka nnope."
  88,5,"Sichimwesyedwa mu tutumule jwansemule kusyene."
  88,6,"Ngasakola ŵanganyao yakulya ikaŵeje miŵa janchongwe."
  89,1,"Ngukulumbila kumasikusiku."
  89,2,"Ni ilo likumi (yandanda yamwesi wa Mfungotatu). ",footnotes:1:Akusimulila Ibn Abbâs رضى الله عنه yanti: Ntume ﷺ jwatite: “Pangali masengo gambone gagakutendekwaga m’moŵa ganepe nikuŵa gapenani kugapunda masengo gagakutendekwaga mu aga moŵaga (moŵa likumi gandanda ga mwesi wa Mfungotatu).” Maswahaba gawusyisye kuti: “Namuno Jihâd?” Jwalakwe jwatite: “Namuno Jihâd, ikaŵeje mundu jwakopweche nsyenejo ni chipanje chakwe kuli nkogoya (wa ku Jihâd), ni nganijuwuja ni chilichose, (umi wakwe ni chipanje chakwe yosope imalile ku Jihâdiko).” Swahîh Al-Bukhârî, Hadith No. 926).
  89,3,"Ni (indu yayili) yiŵiliyiŵili kwisa soni (yayili) chimochimo."